rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國官方學者: 美國國務卿反對《逃犯條例》修訂, 未必代表整個「美國決策層」的立場<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1164978/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1164978/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e845e556de396df119884ff2f7be0f64ba22070c","tid":1164984,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"飯民依家要做既應該係向美帝示好"},{"pid":"c97e416cfb862469867ad9371cf5fb0ad5e665ab","tid":1164984,"uid":93000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f82079f3a9c5c1a185812b89535b2a18e04dbacd","tid":1164984,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b2fff645c9e537a7433afc3adfb06ad4f1ce99b","tid":1164984,"uid":93000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"仆街 班建制都仲講大話 真係當D美帝冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"老共: 呢d未必係美帝立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國官方學者: 美國國務卿反對《逃犯條例》修訂, 未必代表整個「美國決策層」的立場<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1164978/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1164978/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"其實諗真D 二戰後各國慢慢都走上正途 為獨中國係冇變 仲要退步中。 人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc946c241f0a30707bd6bfa060c0c1631da98a8d","tid":1164984,"uid":20563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"孽劉個廢閪早幾日話美國取消關係法囉，驚你呀<br />\n而家又話想香港國際地位希望可以保持<br />\n都on79"},{"pid":"b6eda340da34cd70ab812c29d129bc7cadb006c0","tid":1164984,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4af7086a65312c50155f79e39df84c9ce5f6c3","tid":1164984,"uid":93000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc946c241